{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Daemon Targaryen", "slug": "daemon-targaryen", "text": "Lady Jeyne dismissed his claim and warned him from the Vale", "line": 19, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Laena Velaryon", "slug": "laena-velaryon", "text": "Corlys's daughter, a maid of two-and-twenty, tall and lovely, long betrothed to a wastrel son of the Sealord of Braavos", "line": 19, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Laena Velaryon", "slug": "laena-velaryon", "text": "In her final hour she tried to reach Vhagar to fly a last time", "line": 63, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Rhaenyra Targaryen", "slug": "rhaenyra-targaryen", "text": "The king's heir, who bore Lucerys late in 115 AC and Joffrey in 117 AC", "line": 33, "hedge_term": "eustace", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Rhaenyra Targaryen", "slug": "rhaenyra-targaryen", "text": "She grew estranged from Queen Alicent and kept to Dragonstone", "line": 37, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Alicent Hightower", "slug": "alicent-hightower", "text": "The queen, whose rivalry with Rhaenyra deepened past bearing", "line": 37, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Harwin Strong", "slug": "harwin-strong", "text": "Amongst the greens it was an article of faith he, not Laenor, fathered Rhaenyra's sons", "line": 45, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Lyonel Strong", "slug": "lyonel-strong", "text": "The cause was never determined and many blamed foul play", "line": 121, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Larys Strong", "slug": "larys-strong", "text": "Larys the Clubfoot, who became Lord of Harrenhal on the deaths of his father and elder brother", "line": 121, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Larys Strong", "slug": "larys-strong", "text": "Some suspected him of the fire; he later sat the small council as Lord Confessor and master of whisperers", "line": 203, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Corlys Velaryon", "slug": "corlys-velaryon", "text": "He offered ten thousand golden dragons for Laenor's killer", "line": 77, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Joffrey Velaryon", "slug": "joffrey-velaryon", "text": "Rhaenyra's third son, born 117 AC, brown-haired like his brothers", "line": 45, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Otto Hightower", "slug": "otto-hightower", "text": "He remained the King's Hand and led the council as Viserys's strength failed", "line": 203, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Aegon the Elder", "slug": "aegon-ii-targaryen", "text": "Alicent's eldest son, wed to his sister Helaena in 122 AC at fifteen, a lazy glutton and lecher", "line": 145, "hedge_term": "eustace", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Helaena Targaryen", "slug": "helaena-targaryen", "text": "Alicent's daughter, a dragonrider of Dreamfyre, wed to her brother Aegon at thirteen", "line": 145, "hedge_term": "eustace", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Mellos", "slug": "mellos", "text": "Grand Maester and moderating council voice, who hinted at the sons' bastardy and mused the king himself might have ordered the Harrenhal fire", "line": 121, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Orwyle", "slug": "orwyle", "text": "His potions were held more efficacious than Mellos's leechings", "line": 197, "hedge_term": "eustace", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Tyland Lannister", "slug": "tyland-lannister", "text": "Ser, the lord admiral and master of ships, brother to the Lord of Casterly Rock", "line": 203, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Lyman Beesbury", "slug": "lyman-beesbury", "text": "The aged Lord, master of coin almost without interruption since the Old King's day", "line": 203, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
{"unit": "fab-heirs-of-the-dragon-15-p03", "kind": "prose", "entity": "Criston Cole", "slug": "criston-cole", "text": "Ser, Lord Commander of the Kingsguard and a bitter foe to Rhaenyra, who tutored Aemond in arms", "line": 203, "hedge_term": "mushroom", "hedge_distance": 0}
